1
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,040
This is her fate.

2
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,400
I can't beat them.

3
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,800
But can't I just run away?

4
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:11,200
Chase them!

5
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,440
All of you, chase them!

6
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:13,200
Hurry!

7
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,039
Hurry up!

8
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:14,880
Go!

9
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:23,480
That place

10
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,160
enshrines the ancestors of the Tu family.

11
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,690
They must not be disturbed!

12
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:27,440
This...

13
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,800
How can this be?

14
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:31,000
Hurry and stop them!

15
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,039
Old Madam!

16
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,520
If you dare to come in,

17
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:35,320
I'll burn down the ancestral hall!

18
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,320
Nobody move!

19
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:39,120
Let's see how you face the ancestors of the Tu family!

20
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:41,520
I'll tear you to pieces!

21
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,920
Catch me first!

22
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:49,680
If we go out now, she'll definitely hack us to death.

23
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,920
Block the ancestral hall!

24
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,120
If they dare to show their heads,

25
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,720
execute them on the spot!

26
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,620
What did I tell you?

27
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,200
Qiuyue.

28
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,720
Young Master Liu.

29
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,760
Thank you.

30
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,320
But you should just hand me over.

31
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:05,800
This is my fate.

32
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,120
I accept it.

33
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,600
What are you talking about?

34
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,120
Fate is in your own hands.

35
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,720
Sometimes we can give our lives

36
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,640
for the right thing,

37
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:15,000
but definitely not in such a senseless way.

38
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,760
If we can find Master Tu's head

39
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,160
and catch the real killer,

40
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:20,320
maybe we can convince Old Madam Tu to spare Yunmeng.

41
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,250
But right now...

42
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,360
There is always a way out.

43
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,920
Let's split up and look around.

44
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:34,920
See if there's an exit or something.

45
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,120
Ancestors above,

46
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,680
your unfilial descendant Tu Yunmeng

47
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,360
made an unintentional mistake.

48
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,400
By practicing necromancy without permission,

49
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,280
I brought disaster

50
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,720
and caused the death of my own father.

51
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,120
I am willing to bear all the consequences.

52
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,780
Please do not involve others.

53
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,920
Who voluntarily takes the blame?

54
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:52,960
If you just give up,

55
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,490
wouldn't my help be in vain?

56
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,450
How could you...

57
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,120
He's just like this,

58
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,400
talking nonsense all day long.

59
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,400
But some things he says

60
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,320
actually make sense.

61
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,080
Anyway,

62
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,610
don't beat yourself up.

63
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,360
Learn from your grandmother.

64
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,800
Driving others crazy is the secret to a long, healthy life.

65
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,720
I think your grandfather

66
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,760
probably died very early.

67
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,760
How do you know?

68
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,320
Did you know my grandfather?

69
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:14,640
Did you just communicate with his spirit?

70
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:15,800
Hopeless.

71
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:29,380
Very few people should come here, right?

72
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,320
How come there are

73
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,460
signs of it being moved recently?

74
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:38,380
It doesn't look like there's any mechanism.

75
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,160
This is...

76
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,840
The ancestors have manifested!

77
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,920
This is science.

78
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:54,180
It has nothing to do with your ancestors.

79
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,280
Vinegar and blood

80
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,920
can produce a chemical reaction,

81
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,450
turning the blood dark red.

82
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,720
Certain substances in the wine

83
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:02,780
can make this reaction more obvious.

84
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,960
Why are there bloodstains here?

85
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:09,170
Could Master Tu's head be hidden here?

86
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:11,880
Judging from the direction of the blood spatter,

87
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,000
that should be it.

88
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,519
Incense ash can cover up the smell of a corpse.

89
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,880
As for who hid Master Tu's head here,

90
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,440
we'll know once we check the fingerprints.

91
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,500
It looks like a mechanism.

92
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,860
All right, let me do it.

93
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,320
If they don't come out, smoke them to death.

94
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:09,180
The Tu family will not allow this scandal to spread.

95
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:09,920
Hurry.

96
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:13,650
Yunmeng.

97
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,320
Where is this?

98
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,520
Let me see.

99
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,580
You scared me to death.

100
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,730
Yunmeng, just hold onto me.

101
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,680
What is this place?

102
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,840
Judging from the condition of the wax,

103
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,320
people must come here often.

104
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:07,420
It seems someone specifically prepared them here.

105
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,640
I've never heard anyone mention

106
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,810
that there is such a place in the house.

107
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:15,050
It seems the Tu family is hiding many secrets.

108
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,200
Smoke them to death.

109
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,060
Don't let a single one escape.

110
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,500
If we don't get out, we'll choke to death.

111
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,120
Going back means death too.

112
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,159
What should we do?

113
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,640
This is fate.

114
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,120
What fate?

115
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,200
You are so young.

116
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,010
Fate is in your own hands, okay?

117
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,320
Instead of blaming others,

118
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:42,450
you might as well do something useful.

119
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,640
I have an idea.

120
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,680
This anti-smoke method...

121
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,210
I've seen someone teach it.

122
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,850
I'd rather choke to death than do that.

123
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:04,120
It means there is still a way down.

124
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,920
Let's go.

125
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:05,880
Hold this.

126
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,840
Be careful.

127
00:07:32,400 --> 00:07:34,060
Why are there so many mummies?

128
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,760
This place

129
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,420
is dry and ventilated,

130
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,300
making it perfect for hiding bodies.

131
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,640
This is also

132
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,800
the purpose of building this place.

133
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,440
This is a contract for a pawned wife.

134
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,930
Could it be that they are all...

135
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,720
Yunmeng.

136
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,050
Yunmeng, what's wrong?

137
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:03,000
Yunmeng.

138
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,160
Yunmeng.

139
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,680
My mother was also a pawned wife.

140
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:32,000
Back then, because she couldn't give birth to a son,

141
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,659
my mother was beaten to death.

142
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,280
I've never found her remains.

143
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,240
I can't find my mother.

144
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,000
Just because she couldn't have a son,

145
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,080
they were so cruel.

146
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,690
They are simply beasts.

147
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,840
In his eyes,

148
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,360
women are just tools for reproduction,

149
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:55,160
which is why he would do something like pawning a wife to have a child.

150
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,360
And these mummies,

151
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,840
some

152
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,500
have been here for a few years,

153
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,160
others

154
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,400
for decades.

155
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,400
At that time...

156
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,480
Master Tu is brutally harming these people.

157
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,000
Yes.

158
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,760
Look at the dates.

159
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:13,370
The earliest goes back to the Taizong era.

160
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,640
That means,

161
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,400
pawning wives

162
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:18,760
has been a tradition in the Tu family.

163
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,040
And most of them

164
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,490
died unnatural deaths.

165
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,530
Generations have harmed women like this.

166
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,130
If it isn't made public,

167
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,760
it would be intolerable to heaven.
